T02TD2458E:132b-1: yo ga laksha na sa tya /
T02TD2458E:132b-3: rnal 'byor gyi mtshan nyid bden pa /
T02TD2458E:132b-4: rje btsun ma sgrol ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2458E:132b-5: phyogs bcu dus kun sangs rgyas dang //
T02TD2458E:132b-6: chos dang dge 'dun tshogs bcas la //
T02TD2458E:132b-7: thal sbyar gus pas phyag 'tshal nas //
T02TD2458E:132b-8: rnal 'byor bsgom pa'i man ngag ni ;
T02TD2458E:132b-9: / rin chen sna tshogs tshogs pa ltar //
T02TD2458E:132b-10: rnal 'byor pa rnams sgrol ba'i phyir //
T02TD2458E:132b-11: mdor bsdus nas ni bshad par bya //
T02TD2458E:132b-12: nam gyi cha smad gnyid las sad //
T02TD2458E:132b-13: bdag ma gtogs pa'i sems can la //
T02TD2458E:132b-14: thog ma nyid du snying rje bsgom //
T02TD2458E:132b-15: de nas bdag nyid la bltas nas //
T02TD2458E:133a-2: slong ba'i sems can dag la ni //
T02TD2458E:133a-3: ji srid 'ongs kyang ser sna yi //
T02TD2458E:133a-4: dri mas mi gos nyid du bya //
T02TD2458E:133a-5: gal te bslab pa las 'gal ba'i //
T02TD2458E:133a-6: yid la rgyu ba phra mo yang //
T02TD2458E:133a-7: bsam pa nyid du mi bya na //
T02TD2458E:133a-8: ngag dang lus kyi smos ci dgos //
T02TD2458E:133a-9: bdag la di ring khro ba dang //
T02TD2458E:133a-10: brdeg pa la sogs 'byung bar shog / des kyang 'khrug par mi bya'o //
T02TD2458E:133a-11: le lo byung na shes bzhin gyis //
T02TD2458E:133a-12: mgo la me 'bar bzhin du dor //
T02TD2458E:133a-14: spyod lam ji ltar gnas 'dug kyang //
T02TD2458E:133a-15: yid ni lha yi nga rgyal dang //
T02TD2458E:133a-16: skad cig tsam yang mi 'bral bar //
T02TD2458E:133a-17: rang nyid yin par rtag tu bsam //
T02TD2458E:133a-19: shes dang shes bya bdag gis ni //
T02TD2458E:133a-20: de ring nyid nas bdag gis brtag / bstod dang smad pa grags ma grags //
T02TD2458E:133a-21: gzhan dag ji ltar zer yang ni //
T02TD2458E:133a-22: de nyid brag ca lta bu dang //
T02TD2458E:133a-23: 'on pa lta bu bdag gis bya //
T02TD2458E:133a-24: chags pa'i gzugs sgra dri ro reg /'dod yon lnga la gang du yang //
T02TD2458E:133a-25: rnam shes 'phro ba'i yul byung yang //
T02TD2458E:133a-26: ngag tu ma thon bar du bzlog / gzugs su snang rnams sku nyid yin //
T02TD2458E:133a-27: sgra rnams gsung du bdag nyid brtag / sems can byang chub rgyu yin phyir //
T02TD2458E:133a-28: de yi shes pa ye shes yin //
T02TD2458E:133a-29: sems can ji ltar mthong gyur kyang //
T02TD2458E:133a-30: de dag nyid la blo phyag bya //
T02TD2458E:133a-31: 'di dag nyid la brten nas bdag / sangs rgyas nyid du 'grub pas na //
T02TD2458E:133a-32: dge ba'i bshes gnyen dam pa yin //
T02TD2458E:133a-33: mang po tshogs par gyur pa na //
T02TD2458E:133a-34: ro dang dur khrod 'du shes bskyed //
T02TD2458E:133a-35: grong du 'jug par byed pa na //
T02TD2458E:133a-36: btson ra khri mon 'du shes bskyed //
T02TD2458E:133a-37: rgyal po'i pho brang 'gro ba na //
T02TD2458E:133a-39: g-yang sa chen po'i 'du shes bskyed //
T02TD2458E:133a-40: gal te bud med tshogs mthong na //
T02TD2458E:133a-41: mi gtsang rdzas ni sum cu dang //
T02TD2458E:133a-43: nye du pha ma bu tsha rnams //
T02TD2458E:133a-44: de la chags spangs btang snyoms bsam //
T02TD2458E:133a-45: dgra rnams mthong na 'di dag gis //
T02TD2458E:133a-46: bzod rdzogs byang chub yin par bsam //
T02TD2458E:133a-47: bdag gi longs spyod rdzas la yang //
T02TD2458E:133a-48: 'dir ni rtsod pa'i rgyu dang ni //
T02TD2458E:133b-1: bdag la bstod pa brjod na yang //
T02TD2458E:133b-4: gal te smod pa byung na yang //
T02TD2458E:133b-5: 'di la bzod bsgom byang chub kyang //
T02TD2458E:133b-6: mtshan ma rdzogs par rab tu bsam //
T02TD2458E:133b-7: gnas la zhen pa byung gyur na //
T02TD2458E:133b-8: rmi lam grong khyer ji bzhin du //
T02TD2458E:133b-9: rnal 'byor pa yis rab tu bsgom //
T02TD2458E:133b-10: bdag gis deng gi nyin zhig la //
T02TD2458E:133b-11: ngag las bzlas brjod kha ton bya //
T02TD2458E:133b-12: klag sogs bslab las mi 'gal bar //
T02TD2458E:133b-13: de ring bdag gis smra bar bya //
T02TD2458E:133b-14: lus kyi g-yo ba thams cad kyang //
T02TD2458E:133b-15: mchod dang bskor ba la sogs pa //
T02TD2458E:133b-16: ngal so don yong nyid du bya //
T02TD2458E:133b-17: rnam rtog gnyen por ma bsdams na //
T02TD2458E:133b-18: tshig tu brjod pas ci zhig 'grub //
T02TD2458E:133b-19: de bas rnam pa thams cad du //
T02TD2458E:133b-20: gnyen po'i dpung tshogs bskyed nas ni //
T02TD2458E:133b-21: nyon mongs rnams ni dbyis phyin bya //
T02TD2458E:133b-22: bza' btung zhim bo za ba'i tshe //
T02TD2458E:133b-23: rol zhen pa spang bya zhing //
T02TD2458E:133b-24: mi gtsang rgyu las byung ba dang //
T02TD2458E:133b-25: tha mar mi gtsang 'gyur bar bsam //
T02TD2458E:133b-26: reg bya 'jam po tshor ba'i tshe //
T02TD2458E:133b-27: reg bya ji bzhin yin par bsam //
T02TD2458E:133b-28: 'dir mang smos pa ci zhig dgos //
T02TD2458E:133b-29: gang du nyon mongs 'phel ba yi //
T02TD2458E:133b-30: khyim pa'ang rab tu byung yang rung //
T02TD2458E:133b-31: de dag rab tu spang bya zhing //
T02TD2458E:133b-32: nyon mongs rnam par mi 'phel ba'i //
T02TD2458E:133b-33: sgrub pa'i grogs mchog gang yang rung //
T02TD2458E:133b-34: de dag bsten pa mig ltar bya //
T02TD2458E:133b-35: bdag ni de ring nas brtsams te //
T02TD2458E:133b-36: byang chub snying por mchis bar du //
T02TD2458E:133b-37: rtag tu rab tu byung ba dang //
T02TD2458E:133b-38: tshangs par spyod pa nyid du bya //
T02TD2458E:133b-39: nyin mtshan dus las ma yol bar //
T02TD2458E:133b-40: thun mtshams gsum du bsgom par bya //
T02TD2458E:133b-41: srog dang rtsol ba bkag pa dang //
T02TD2458E:133b-42: rlung med pa yi mar me ltar //
T02TD2458E:133b-43: rtag tu spros bral bsgom bar bya //
T02TD2458E:133b-44: de nas ldang tshe nga rgyal gyis //
T02TD2458E:133b-45: mtshan dang dpe byad skur ldan pa'i //
T02TD2458E:133b-46: lha yi nga rgyal brtan por bsam //
T02TD2458E:133b-47: mtshan mo'i thun la bab pa'i tshe //
T02TD2458E:133b-48: bde gshegs ji ltar gzims pa ltar //
T02TD2458E:133b-49: 'jig rten rtog spangs bdag nyid nyal //
T02TD2458E:133b-50: mdor na chos rnams thams cad kun //
T02TD2458E:133b-51: rmi lam lta bur brtag par bya //
T02TD2458E:133b-52: rnal 'byor sgom rnams gtsor bya yis //
T02TD2458E:133b-53: lus ngag dge ba gtsod mi bya //
T02TD2458E:134a-2: nyon mongs pas ni ma yengs par //
T02TD2458E:134a-3: bsgrims nas bdag gis 'bad pas bsgrub //
T02TD2458E:134a-4: rtag tu 'chi bsam ma chags blos //
T02TD2458E:134a-5: dngos po ci la'ang ma chags par //
T02TD2458E:134a-6: spyod lam ji ltar gnas kyang bsgom //
T02TD2458E:134a-7: bsod nams sems can kun la bsngo //
T02TD2458E:134a-8: byang chub bzang po bdag gis ni //
T02TD2458E:134a-9: rnal 'byor sgom pa brtsams pa yis //
T02TD2458E:134a-10: dge bzla zer dri med des //
T02TD2458E:134a-11: bdag dang 'gro ba ma lus pas //
T02TD2458E:134a-12: dpal ldan rdo rje 'chang 'grub shog / rnal 'byor gyi mtshan nyid bden pa mkhas pa chen po dpal byang chub bzang po'i zhal snga nas mdzad pa rdzogs so//
